{
 "name": "RPlog_Simone_Drake_Meets_with_Sabbath",
 "title": "Simone Drake Meets with Sabbath",
 "summary": "In the darkened Prex's office of CSA Headquarters on Etti IV, the Corporate Sector executive Simone Drake returns with her Espo guards and her dog Duke to find the Imperial agent Sabbath waiting in the shadows. Sabbath reveals he has come on his own initiative -- without Grand Moff Caldny's knowledge -- to take the captive Han Solo off the CSA's hands and end its games between Empire and Rebellion. Drake, wary of the New Republic fleet threatening to level Etti IV, negotiates the terms of a quiet handover, and Sabbath assures her his unmarked ship and the incoming Imperial fleet make the transfer safe, with the Rebels easily fooled into believing Solo was simply kidnapped. The two agree to arrange the transfer the following evening, and Sabbath departs with a smirk.",
